LWE-Polynomial 0.1 -- Learning-With-Errors-based Encryption System --
======================================================================

LWE-Polynomial is an implementation of the polynomial ring-based LWE cryptosystem,
developed by Richard Lindner and Chris Peikert in "Better Key Sizes (and Attacks) 
for LWE-Based Encryption"(2010).

AUTHOR
======

Norman Lahr (norman@lahr.email)


